name: 10k Stablepizza
description: Because it's more fun to hold a bronze Pizza instead of 10k Tokens. A limited edition Pizza only available for a limited time in the RareDough Shop. Owners of this NFT are eligible to receive 10010 BREAD Tokens (0.1% Bonus), if burned in the NFT Oven. Final supply is determined based on Sales during the Sale period. Burn-Oven is enabled AFTER Sale ends.
